item.title: 4 new compiler errors. HELP!
item.dc:creator: @sp3c sp3c
item.description:
@sp3c wrote:

Simple, find what it says in the pic in client.java. Which would be the line should be placed on top in context menu just do ctr+f and type in: should be placed on top in context menu and then add a ; at the end like this: should be placed on top in context menu; It’s saying to do that, but u probably just need to add a // in front like this: //should be placed on top in context menu
If you get any errors ask me.

Also some sources dont allow u to see ur own crown, like testscape.
And post ur pickup command from client.java
